name: !BROCKBROCK!
description:
This needs to end! There are people who appreciate wiping themselves in the ass, and really small children who can not dance and smile at the same time! And there are actually animals that do not have hair and that cough nervously every time someone looks at it! And there are siblings who have never been allowed to open a gift without bleeding nosebleeds! Have you ever thought about that?! Think about it the next time you draw your stupid shit! There is actually NOTHING to laugh about to begin with! 
NOTHING!
